    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 93.</p><p>Tier I: Heroic Sharpshooter</p><p>Sniper’s Range. While using a ranged weapon, you double its normal and long range. Your ranged weapon attacks ignore half and three-quarters cover.</p><p>Pinning Shot. Once per round, when you hit a Huge or smaller creature with a ranged weapon attack, you can choose to pin them. The creature’s speed is reduced by 20 feet until the end of its next turn.</p><p>Greater Accuracy. Your ranged weapon attacks cannot be made at disadvantage, and your critical range is increased by 1 for attacks made with ranged weapons.</p></div>",
